title: Steve Jobs step down as CEO of Apple
description:
Steve Jobs will No Longer CEO Of Apple

A major development in Cupertino: Apple CEO Steve Jobs has stepped down, the board named Tim Cook as his replacement. The company said "Steve's extraordinary vision and leadership saved Apple and guided it to its position as the world's most innovative and valuable technology company."

Steve himself published the following letter:

" I have always said if there ever came a day when I could no longer meet my duties and expectations as Apple's CEO, I would be the first to let you know. Unfortunately, that day has come.

I hereby resign as CEO of Apple. I would like to serve, if the Board sees fit, as Chairman of the Board, director and Apple employee.

As far as my successor goes, I strongly recommend that we execute our succession plan and name Tim Cook as CEO of Apple.

I believe Apple's brightest and most innovative days are ahead of it. And I look forward to watching and contributing to its success in a new role.

I have made some of the best friends of my life at Apple, and I thank you all for the many years of being able to work alongside you."

Steve
Apple has confirmed that Jobs will stay on as Chairman.

description:
Bill shows you how to install this Redline Tuning Bolt-In QuickLIFT PLUS Hood Strut Kit on your 2015-2017 V6, EcoBoost or GT Mustang.

Product Link: http://www.cjponyparts.com/redline-tuning-hood-strut-kit-quicklift-plus-bolt-in-2015-2016/p/HDGL24/

In this video we are installing a set of Redling Tuning QuickLIFT PLUS hood struts on a 2015 Mustang GT.  We were a little surprised when we looked under the hood of the new S550 Mustang and found a prop rod. Not only are these ugly to look at, but they often get in the way when working under the hood. Thankfully with the help of Redline Tuning, this can be a rather quick fix.

Installation is easy and only takes a few minutes, however, you will have to drill a small hole into the factory battery cover. Once installed though, say goodbye to the ugly factory prop rod and hello to a clean looking engine bay.

title: APB: All Points Bulletin Video Review
description:
Full text review: 

http://www.gamervision.com/users/jonathan_h_cooper/articles/apb_all_points_bulletin_pc_

Realtime Worlds has been busy. After shipping Crackdown for the Xbox 360, they decided to create something a bit more ambitious. With David Jones, one of the creators of the original Grand Theft Auto,  handling lead design duties, the developer has been hard at work on All Points Bulletin, or APB. Often referred to as the "GTA  MMO" (though not by the developer), the game brings a number of fresh ideas to the table, hoping to mesh together shooters and MMO games into a persistent world never before attempted.

description: Tim Gredley started life in the show ring and progressed to jumping. ***PLEASE READ!!! AND WATCH IN HQ*** 

NOTE: I AM NOT YET BACK  ON YOUTUBE. I UPLOADED THIS VIDEO ON AUGUST 27TH BUT AS A PRIVATE VIDEO AS I KNEW I WOULDN'T HAVE INTERNET TO UPLOAD IT BY SEPTEMBER 11TH. I THEN WENT TO SOMEONE'S HOUSE ON THE DAY OF MY YOUTUBE ANNIVERSARY (SEPTEMBER 11TH) AND MADE IT PUBLIC THEN. BUT I HAVEN'T GOT MANY VIEWS AS CAUSE IT WAS FIRST PUBLIC, IT HASN'T APPEARED ON MY SUBSCRIBERS SUBSCRIPTIONS BOX SO PLEASE SPREAD THE WORD ABOUT THIS VIDEO. THANKS
I WILL HOPFULLY BE BACK BY THE END OF THE SEPTEMBER! :)
--------------------------

Wow, one year on youtube today (Although it's not one year since I started making videos) 
So this video is dedicated to LOTS of people: 
ALL of my subscribers - You're all brilliant and I couldn't of done this without you 
All of my youtube friends - You're all amazing and have really supported me. Special thanks to TheOncomingStorm07, Lee from Vortexguyz934 and DWGigoogledpie (She's also ConverseCrevasseGirl and a member of vortexguyz934) 
And also all of my Canadian Friends - This video is mainly dedicated to you canadians and I'm really going to miss you all. Like the lyrics say "Thanks for the memories" Lol. I know that four of you have youtube 
Vicky - http://www.youtube.com/user/muffin412410 Kailey - http://www.youtube.com/user/KaileyLeBlanc Emma - http://www.youtube.com/user/converse0freak1 
Heather  http://www.youtube.com/user/alicecullenwannabe
So I know only Vicky likes doctor who so the video won't make as much sense to you others but its still dedicated to you all ;) 

So anyway, back to the description; I've had a great time on youtube and made some amazing friends so this video is basically to celebrate the fact that I've been on youtube for one year and just to thank all of you. 
The song is perfect because it's one year on youtube so "Thanks for the memories" to all my youtube friends and I'm moving so "Thanks for the memories" to all of my Canadian Friends I hope you all enjoy this 
Because I'm not sure if I'll have internet again by September 11th, I've uploaded this video on Sunday August 17th but made it a private video and on September 11th, I'll go to a friends house and make it public ;) 
I hope you like it, I think it's one of my best videos yet
There were a few glitches which I fixed but unfortunately, to fix them, I had to get rid of some cool effects :( 
Anyway, enjoy :D

title: Su Amor Me Hace Vivir - Musicap
description:
El 2 de Mayo del 2009 se presentaron el Coro Musicap y el Coro de Campanas en la Iglesia Adventista del 7° Día de San Martin, Buenos Aires, Argentina. 
Cabe destacar que se pudo ver el resultado del esfuerzo no sólo de los interpretes, sino también de todos aquellos que colaboraron en las más variadas actividades que se tuvieron que realizar para llevar adelante el evento (limpieza, preparación, decoración, audio, luces, etc, etc,etc). A todos los que de alguna manera participaron e hicieron posible éste evento: MUCHAS GRACIAS!!!
Es una alegría poder compartir éste material y agradezco a Dios por haberlo hecho posible y a Denny Luz por permitirme compartirlo.
Qué Dios nos bendiga, guíe y acompañe!!!
Con cariño!!!
P@blin

CORO MUSICAP

El Coro de la Universidad Adventista del Plata, también conocido como MUSICAP, está integrado por alumnos que a la par de sus actividades académicas dedican tiempo y esfuerzo para el canto. 

Este Coro, fundado en 1922, ha actuado en las principales salas de nuestro país, como el Teatro Colón, Auditorio Belgrano, Teatro de las Provincias Argentinas, Teatro Astral, Teatro Odeón, Teatro El Círculo de Rosario y Teatro San Martín de Córdoba, entre otros.

A partir de 1976 el Coro realizó numerosas giras por el exterior, presentando su repertorio de variados géneros y estilos: música sacra, clásica y canciones folklóricas populares argentinas, sudamericanas, centroamericanas, Estados Unidos y Canadá.
Su director actual es el Mg. Denny Luz, quien cursó sus estudios en el Instituto Superior Adventista del Plata, egresando con los títulos de Profesor Superior de Canto y Profesor Nacional de Música con especialidad en Piano. Cursó estudios de posgrado en la Universidad de Andrews, USA, donde obtuvo el título de Master of Music con especialidad en dirección coral. Ha realizado numerosos cursos de perfeccionamiento y capacitación tanto en el área artística como docente. Como director de agrupaciones corales actúa regularmente presentando obras del repertorio universal de todas las épocas, con especial interés en la música sacra. Como solista (tenor) ha actuado en diversas obras del repertorio sinfónico coral como la Cantanta 140 y Magnificat en Re Mayor de J.S. Bach, Dixit Dominus y Chandos Anthem de G.F. Haendell, Sinfonía Lobgesang de F. Mendelssohn y Pasión según San Juan de Arvo Pärt, con agrupaciones orquestales como la Orquesta Sinfónica de Entre Ríos, Orquesta Sinfónica Provincial de Santa Fe, Michiana Symphony Orchestra, St. Joseph Pro Music Chamber Orchestra, bajo la batuta de destacados directores. Alterna sus actividades artísticas con la docencia en el Departamento de Música de la Universidad Adventista del Plata.

CORO DE CAMPANAS

El Coro de Campanas de la Universidad Adventista del Plata está integrado por un set de 49 campanas que abarca un total de cuatro octavas. Cada campana, construida con una aleación especial de metales, está afinada en un solo sonido determinado. Los instrumentistas ejecutan entre dos y siete campanas según las exigencias de las diferentes obras. El repertorio de este conjunto abarca obras clásicas universales, sacras, y danzas y canciones del folklore sudamericano.

A lo largo de su existencia se ha presentado en diversas salas, teatros, festivales, y encuentros corales, catedrales, escuelas, exposiciones literarias, emisoras de radio y canales de televisión del territorio argentino, uruguayo, paraguayo y brasileño.

Su director actual es el Prof. Daniel Biaggi, quien cursó sus estudios en el Instituto Superior Adventista del Plata, egresando con los títulos de Profesor Nacional de Música con especialidad en Piano y Profesor de Música con especialidad en clarinete. Además ha participado en clases magistrales, cursos y talleres corales con reconocidos maestros a nivel nacional e internacional.

title: Origami Owl Top Earner Secrets: Improve Your Origami Owl Profits
description:
http://www.MeetSteveJaffe.com?k=Origami_Owl  Get Your FREE Ebook Plus 8 Training Videos.  Learn To Be A Top Earner In Origami Owl

Origami Owl business owners: It's time to learn what it REALLY takes to become a top 2% producer Are you determined to making it to the top of your comp. plan?

If you seek to become a top earner, it's vital you get way beyond merely talking to colleagues, associates, family and friends about your business..

You MUST learn to market!

Here are 3 strategies 7-figure income earners use to build network marketing empires today:

- Drive A Lot Of Internet Traffic

Shopping malls and stores depend on customers to enter their stores. Store sales goes up when more people enter the store. This has a lot of similarity to your Origami Owl enterprise. Getting more visitors to your website will increase the number of leads you create.

Your Origami Owl income will increase as the number of leads you generate increases. Top earners generally attract more traffic and leads than everybody else. Top producers in network marketing average 30-200 leads per day on the internet.

Most everybody else in opportunities like Origami Owl creates 0-2 leads a day online. So how do you produce lots of targeted traffic to help you become a Origami Owl top producer?

You've got to build ONE traffic source at a time. You can get traffic from Youtube, Facebook, Twitter, Google or many other sources. Select and focus on ONE traffic source until you generate 20 leads per day or more from that traffic source. Never add another source of traffic until you reach this threshold.

New marketers get in over their head by taking on too much, too fast. This is a huge mistake. These people get overwhelmed and then quit. Only pursue one traffic strategy at first.

- Automate Your Follow-Up With Email

As soon as you create a lead for your Origami Owl opportunity, telephone your lead exactly the same day (preferably, the same hour), while your lead is still fresh. Ask questions to get a perspective on what your prospect is looking for.|Listen more than you speak. Question the prospect about what it is they're looking for.|Don't talk too much. Instead ask questions and listen to learn what issues and challenges the prospect is facing in his business.|Rather than explaining or talking a lot, simply ask questions about what the prospect is seeking. Listen. Evaluate if this is somebody you want in your Origami Owl organization.

Follow up with automated, pre-written emails in addition to connecting with people on the phone. In your emails, take the role of a teacher. Relate practical advice and tactics people can apply in their businesses to improve their results.

Teach about lead generation, recruiting and retention tactics, or any other pertinent topics. Every email should include a call to action to the next part of your Origami Owl exposure process. 

Email follow up:

- Is an addition to , not a replacement for, calling leads on the phone

- Is automated marketing that goes to work for you while you do other things

- Allows you to craft the ideal marketing message for your Origami Owl business

Use an """"autoresponder"""", a service that send your pre written emails on autopilot.

- Attract Prospects To You As Opposed To Approaching Them

Lots of people in companies like Origami Owl are taught to approach friends, colleagues and others about their business. This is an easy method, but you're going to run out of people to approach in a few weeks. 

Marketers start chasing after people at events, in stores, and at restaurants to try to get them into their business. aaproaching strangers about your business is not going to create solid results. What are the odds a total stranger is going to be interested in and have the skills to thrive in your Origami Owl business? Pretty slim.

Forget approaching total strangers about Origami Owl. Get prospects to approach YOU about Origami Owl. Attracting prospects to you creates several advantages:

- You'll get more signups per conversation. You make more money with fewer hassles.

À la fin de la vidéo, un des trous a une forme étrange.
On devine un T ... superposé d'un K. ...    TK ...  

Trop fort mon subconscient !

description:

This is the first of five playlists on a project called "Four River Pebbles" accomplished on white Stonehenge paper with Prismacolor Colored Pencils and Caran d'Ache Neocolor II Artist Crayons. The final artwork measures 5"x6". Each playlist introduces new applications of the Icarus technique and can be approached individually at your own pace. 

The project is broken into the following 5 sequential playlists:

1. Beige Pebble

title: GTA: State Of Liberty Online (SOL-O) - First Development Video - Vehicle Sync
description:
http://www.gtasolonline.com
http://forum.gtasolonline.com

http://www.facebook.com/pages/GTA-State-Of-Liberty-Online-SOL-O/114619601915911

Please Like/Favorite/Share with your buddies on Facebook/Twitter/MySpace/Bebo etc. and spread the word.

Thank you!
---------------

It's here, as promised! We have kept the project's momentum going with our first-ever SOL-O development video edition.

This edition focuses on one main core multi-player feature; synchronization.

The main area demonstrated is vehicles, showcasing motion (velocity, movement and turning/rotation), damage, and color.

Ever since the merge of Vice City Online with State Of Liberty, the motion-wise vehicle synchronization has been completely redone, employing new methods to accommodate not only smooth actions, but also extreme circumstances.  Accuracy has been our newest concern, so that's been preserved too, as demonstrated by some tests (skidding, barrel rolls) that are showcased in this video.

With color synchronization, the full spectrum of RGB can be used to color your car (both primary and secondary car color parameters), and further than that, you can set the vehicle's alpha (transparency) - something that has never been accomplished in Vice City before! A simple function in Lua can be used to set all these parameters.

Our vehicle damage synchronization is precision-grade, with each individual panel, door, tyre and light having its own configurable damage status. In addition to manually setting the component states, they are automatically synchronized. Some damage statuses include in-tact, dented, removed/turned on or off, popped, and swinging open.

This video was filmed on November 17, 2010. At no point in the video was the filmer driving.


Filmed and edited by DECEiFER.

title: Error: The communication link is lost - TkFileExplorer
description:
Error: The communication link is lost

If you have this problem, just do the following.

Close the program TkFileExplorer & CLOSE SAMSUNG PC STUDIO.
                                   
Go to your phone and type in Dial: *#6984125*# (These numbers may change depending on the brand and model of your cellphone)

Press: Internals

Master key: *#9072461*#  (These numbers may change depending on the brand and model of your cellphone)

After this you will have many options within the Internals. 

Press Debug Settings.

Within Debug Settings, choose: 'Reboot'.

After you click Reboot, don't click anywhere until it reboots and asks you for the PIN.

All this procedure should be done with your cellphone connected to your computer. Do not pull the USB out.

After you reboot the cell phone open up the program TkFileExplorer and connect the cellphone to the program.

DONE =)

If this procedure didn't work, post a comment telling me that, so that I can explain you another way of solving the problem.

Thanks for watching (I hope I was useful) and good luck =)

title: Blender 3D FPS
description:
WATCH MY NEW VIDEOS!


A game-play video of my WIP first person shooter. Martinesh's filters (bloom and bleach used here). apologies for the low quality, and the music is Kalimba from Ninja Tuna. A small scrap of game art tagged to the end. All Blender (modelling, texturing, scripting, etc) there are no enemies - i do have a bundle of enemy rigs which work, i just ahvent put them in the level yet. few bugs with solutions - tank is very sensitive because i forgot to increase the rotational damping after lowering it in a quick test), the uvmap of the island needs unwrapping again - hence the tiling underwater, the lag is because recording, of course.

Also, the water uses a script  made which deforms mesh based on vertex colour, so its very generic, could be used for crude destruction, grass, trees, water (im going to make a script to dynamically change the vertex colours based on collisions to be used in conjunction, however its quite inefficient, i may try usng a for loop and only having the scrpt triggered once. and may relucantly release the script on Blenderartists at a later date.

PS - this is now way out of date in terms of the progress it shows.

PSPS-RIP project :'( you shall be avenged in the form of a bigger, and better project, and the recycle bin shall pay with it's right to be on the desktop!

Ральф — второстепенный персонаж восьмибитовой компьютерной игры, и ему надоело находиться в тени главного героя, мастера на все руки Феликса, который всегда появляется, чтобы «исправить» ситуацию! После десяти лет добросовестной работы в роли злодея, в течение которых все похвалы выпадали на долю Феликса, Ральф больше не хочет быть плохим.

Он решает отправиться в путешествие по аркадным играм разных жанров, чтобы доказать всем, что и он тоже может быть героем. На своем пути Ральф встречает героев разных игр — хладнокровную сержанта Калхун из игры Hero's Duty, оберегающую планету от нашествия инопланетных захватчиков, и сладкую на вид, но острую на язычок Сластену фон Дю, чье существование в гоночном симуляторе Sugar Rush внезапно оказывается под угрозой. title: FF13 Mission 30 シュファクス & ヌミダエ ×26(?) (35秒) ★5攻略 [PS3/jp]
tags: ['FF13', 'FF13 シュファクス', 'シュファクス', 'FF13 Mission 30', 'シュファクス 攻略', 'シュファクス ガチ狩り', 'FF13 攻略', 'FF XIII 攻略', 'FINAL FANTASY XIII 攻略', 'FINAL FANTASY XIII Mission 30', 'FINAL FANTASY XIII', 'FINAL FANTASY']
description:
難易度 ★★★☆☆

色々と試行錯誤して装備を変えてみた結果・・・



・・・タイム変わってねぇし。＿|￣|◯||| (ｶﾞｸｯ

最初このミッションは30秒切る気満々で挑んだのですが以外に時間がかかってしまいますね。

この戦闘はヌミダエをある程度葬るとシュファクスが現れますが、その瞬間にターゲットがシュファクスになっているかどうかがポイント。
シュファクスが現れるシーンでヌミダエがターゲットだとこちらで照準を合わせないといけないのでその分タイムロスに。
シュファクスはブレイクすると新たなヌミダエを呼ばなくなるので、現れたらシュファクスに狙いを集中してブラスターでさっさとブレイクするのが吉。

オプティマチェンジはシュファクスが現れるシーンの時に行えば尺の長いオプティマチェンジシーンがカットされるのでそこもポイントです。

別装備版(同タイム): http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G3ViXs0gRZM


あれからライトさんの友軍放火について検証してみましたが、どうもルインガでヌミダエをぶっ飛ばしまくると全滅してから新たなヌミダエが現れるまでにタイムラグがあるようです。
つまり、ほんの僅かな時間だけ敵が全くいない状態ができて、そのタイミングでルインガを放つことによって味方がぶっ飛ばされてしまうようです。

しかしターゲットはライトニング自身になっているというのに何故か本人には当たらず仲間の二人が喰らってしまうという非道至極な有様に。

バグなわりに結構頻繁に発生するため、このやり方を試す場合はその点をご配慮のうえで挑戦するようお願い致します。

title: 1966 Ford Bronco #6221 Gateway Classic Cars St. Louis
description:
For sale in our St. Louis showroom is a 1966 Ford Bronco. Ford introduced the Bronco in 1966 to complete with Jeep's CJ and International's Scout. Like its competitors, the Bronco had a small wheelbase at 92 inches. The short stance made the truck maneuverable especially in off-road situations. Simplicity in design led to an affordable yet very capable compact 4x4. This particular example is a Bronco Half Cab which features a small utility bed instead of a set of rear seats. The truck has been frame off restored and nicely customized. Up front is a rebuilt 302 CID V8 backed by an automatic transmission. The exterior is finished in bright red and it sits on top of a nice set of 33" meats. Custom roll bar hold 4 off road lights as do custom bumpers front and rear. This truck isn't all show, the 302 breaths through headers and has a 4 barrel carburetor. The four wheel drive works great and transmission shifts smoothly. Inside the truck has been modernized with new seats, modern stereo, and Air Conditioning. If it's not quite warm enough for the A/C, just pop open the sunroof for some fresh air. Early Broncos are becoming harder to find, and this one is solid, nicely restored, and ready to roll. Use it on road, off road, or a little of both. You can see this Bronco in greater detail, including HD video, at www.GatewayClassicCars.com.  Ốp lưng HTC One M8 SGP Ultra Capsule nhựa dẻo trong suốt.

 1 Mẫu ốp lưng chất lượng cao từ Spigen, thương hiệu hàng đầu thế giới về ốp lưng điện thoại.

 Thông thường để bảo vệ máy tốt bạn sẽ chọn 1 chiếc ốp bằng nhựa dẻo còn để giữ dáng máy bạn cần 1 chiếc ốp cứng trong suốt. Với ốp lưng HTC One M8 SGP Ultra Capsule bạn sẽ vừa bảo vệ máy vừa lộ nguyên thiết kế của máy.

 Được làm từ nhựa dẻo cao cấp TPU trùm kín mọi góc cạnh của máy, từ lưng, viền hay đỉnh máy đều được bảo vệ rất tốt, thiết kế dầy dặn cùng đặc đính đàn hồi của nhựa dẻo giúp hạn chế tối đa những tác động có hại từ bên ngoài lên thân máy. Nhựa TPU với khả năng định hình cao giúp bạn cảm giác cầm chắc chắn hơn hẳn những mẫu silicon thông thường và nó có thiết kế rất sắc sảo với độ hoàn thiện cao.

 Ốp lưng được làm ở dạng trong suốt thế nên thiết kế nguyên bản rất đẹp của HTC One M8 sẽ được lộ diện ra ngoài hoàn toàn.

 Tuy nhiên có 1 điểm trừ ở những mẫu thiết kế nhựa dẻo trong đó là nó dễ bị ố vàng sau 1 thời gian sử dụng.

 SGP đã quảng cáo rằng sản phẩm của họ có khả năng chống ố vàng, tuy nhiên với điều kiện khí hậu đặc trưng của Việt Nam thì điều đó cũng không chắc chắn lắm.

 Sản phẩm chính hãng Spigen USA, Made in Korea.

 Có 1 màu trắng trong suốt.

title: Iron Man Power Suit #8 | Starting the Faceplate | James Bruton
tags: ['XRobots', 'Iron', 'man', 'Helmet', 'motorized', 'faceplate', 'and', 'light', 'up', 'eyes', 'electronics', 'mechanics', 'Iron Man (Fictional Character)', 'servo', 'controller', 'pololu', 'mini', 'maestro', 'rs232', 'serial', 'picaxe', 'development', 'board', 'scrim', 'fabric', 'sun', 'glasses', 'mirror', 'how to', 'make an iron man suit', 'helmet', 'Cosplay (Hobby)']
description:
Here are the details of my Iron Man helmet motorized faceplate and light up eyes - lenses which you can also see through.

The biggest challenge making your own Iron Man power suit - that you can actually wear! – is how much detail. Every expects it to look accurate in terms of colour and shaping, and if you’re going to get inside it latches, strapping and so on is a must but… what else?   Do you motorise the faceplate? How much lighting and depth do you give the unibeam? What kind of flexibility and motion do the knees, knuckles and neck need? Well, hopefully you’ll agree I went all out on this Iron Man build.  Let me know what you think in the comments below. 

① GENIUS

No MacArthur grant yet. But while I’m still waiting by the phone for that call, maybe you might patronise me with your Patreon-age. Or, if you’re all out of digital cash just comment on one of my hilarious Instagram pics, pop me a Tweet or generally yell in my direction.

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/xrobots
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/xrobotsuk
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/xrobotsuk/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/xrobotsuk 

Huge thanks to my patrons, without whom my standard of living would drastically decline. Like, inside out Farm Foods bag decline. Plus a very special shoutout to Aleph Objects, Inc who keep me in LulzBot 3D printers and support me via Patreon. https://www.lulzbot.com/

Why not join my community, who are mostly made up of actual geniuses. There’s a Facebook group and everything: https://www.facebook.com/pg/xrobots.c...

② XROBOTS

Former toy designer, current YouTube maker and general robotics, electrical and mechanical engineer, I’m a fan of doing it yourself and innovation by trial and error. My channel is where I share some of my useful and not-so-useful inventions, designs and maker advice. Iron Man is my go-to cosplay, and 3D printing can solve most issues - broken bolts, missing parts, world hunger, you name it.

XRobots is the community around my content where you can get in touch, share tips and advice, and more build FAQs, schematics and designs are also available. 

③ MUSIC AND SFX

The majority of the music and SFX used in my videos is from Epidemic Sound http://share.epidemicsound.com/xrobots

Los Tres Tristes Tigres es un show de comedia musical que consiste en: rutinas, parodias, monólogos, chistes y canciones cómicas e inéditas.

Este grupo está formado por tres jóvenes regiomontanos, Pedro Palacios (guitarra, requinto), Jesús Gallardo (acordeón) y Erick Ibarra (bajo). Siendo de los comediantes mas jóvenes de México y con un humor para todas las edades, con su particular estilo y originalidad han logrado posicionarse en los mejores lugares de comedia en vivo de México.

Este trío cómico le garantiza la diversión pero sobretodo las risas y carcajadas de todo su público. Recientemente alcanzaron fama nacional e internacional gracias a las Redes Sociales como YouTube y Facebook. Han tenido menciones en televisoras como Televisa y TvAzteca así como también en radio y sitios de internet destacados.

El video más popular del trío es "Mi cuenta Nueva", una parodia de la canción "Mi Casa Nueva" de los Invasores de Nuevo León.

This is an active high-wealth flipping guide (money making guide). I will show you how to flip high-wealth items (nex armours, spirit shields and rares). I recommend at least 50m to flip these items. I will make new guides explaining advanced aspects of flipping soon!

FAQ:
How much money can I make a hour?
It depends on many facts: your cash stack, the time of the day, time of the year, how you perform flipping, etc. I usually make 5-10m+ profit/hour with a cash stack of ~800m. 

Another tip: The fact that we cannot sell items back in GE to increase the buy limit has his advantages and disadvantages: the profit margin is bigger, but you can only flip a certain amount of item per 4 hours. title: Angry Birds 2 review (Dutch, BE)
tags: ['Review', 'tablet', 'telefoon', 'gsm', 'mobiel', 'smartphone', 'Nederland', 'Dutch', '2015', 'allaboutphones', 'all about phones', 'Angry Birds (Video Game Series)', 'Puzzle Game (Media Genre)', 'Angry Birds 2', 'Angry Birds (Video Game)', 'Video Game (Industry)', 'Phone', 'Mobile', 'game']
description:
Een paar dagen geleden zag Angry Birds 2 het licht en in deze video brengen wij jou onze review van dit spel. 

Iedereen kent Angry Birds wel. Het is een van de populairste smartphone games op de markt, maar ook al wordt het spel nog altijd veel gespeeld vond Rovio het tijd om een 2de versie op de markt te brengen. Met Angry Birds 2 komen een hele hoop vernieuwingen maar is het spel echt wel een verbetering ten opzichten van de eerste Angry Birds? In deze review video komen wij tot een conclusie hierover! 

Meer reviews vind je in onze playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLH_c2Es_GvrRi2UjmOMWX0f1sUNHcM3MU

Op zoek naar een nieuwe telefoon of tablet? Bekijk onze aanraders in de telekoopwijzer: http://www.allaboutphones.nl/tags/telekoopwijzer.html

Op de website van All About Phones, http://www.allaboutphones.nl/, kun je terecht voor het laatste nieuws en de laatste reviews over smartphones, tablets en accessoires. Dagelijks maken wij nieuws, reviews en video's over alle smartphones van merken als Apple, Samsung, LG, Sony, Huawei en HTC. Daarnaast hebben we een maandelijkse smartphone-koopwijzer, regelmatig achtergrondblogs en komen we iedere week met de TeleWeek en TeleWiki waarin we je bijpraten met het laatste uit de telecommarkt.

Enkele populaire smartphones die wij op dit moment bespreken zijn de Samsung Galaxy S6, HTC One M9, Huawei P8, LG G4 en Apple iPhone 6. Ook goedkopere modellen zoals de Honor 6, Samsung Galaxy A3, Huawei Ascend G7, Microsoft Lumia 535, Alcatel One Touch Pop C7 en Apple iPhone 5c komen bij ons aan bod en tot slot brengen we nog regelmatig vergelijkingen met oude topmodellen zoals de LG G3, Samsung Galaxy S5, Huawei Ascend P7 en Sony Xperia Z3.

title: Gilbert ready for any outcome at Amstel Gold Race
description:
Philippe Gilbert (Omega-Pharma Lotto) said he is ready for any outcome in the finale of Sunday's Amstel Gold Race  and shrugged off the idea that his rivals could stop him winning one of the three Ardennes Classics just as Fabian Cancellara (Leopard Trek) was closely marked and then outmaneuvered in the cobbled classics.

Gilbert won the Amstel Gold Race last year, finished sixth in Fleche-Wallonne and was third in Liege-Bastogne-Liege. He again opted to miss Paris-Roubaix this spring to focus on the Ardennes classics, which cover many of his training roads in the French speaking Wallonne region of Belgium.

title: UNA ROSA COSMICA E LA GALASSIA AGLI ALBORI DELL'UNIVERSO
description:
RIEDIZIONE DI DUE VIDEO 
PUPPIS-A UNA ROSA COSMICA A 7000 ANNI LUCE DAL NOSTRO PIANETA
Circa 3.700 anni fa gli abitanti della Terra avrebbe potuto vedere una nuova stella luminosa nel cielo. Lentamente oscurata alla vista e poi dimenticato, fino a quando gli astronomi moderni poi trovato i suoi resti, la supernova Puppis A. In questa nuova immagine della Nasa Puppis A, che dista 7mila anni luce dalla Terra, appare simile ad una rosa rossa.

UNA GALASSIA DELL'ALBA DEL NOSTRO UNIVERSO
Gli astronomi della NASA usando i telescopi spaziali Spitzer e Hubble hanno scoperto che una delle galassie più distanti conosciute sforna stelle a un ritmo incredibilmente alto. La galassia, chiamata GN-108036, è la più luminosa mai trovata fino ad oggi a così grandi distanze. La galassia, che è stata scoperta e confermata usando telescopi terrestri, dista 12,9 miliardi di anni luce di distanza. I dati di Spitzer e di Hubble sono stati utilizzati per misurare l'alto tasso di produzione di stelle, equivalenti a circa 100 soli all'anno. Per riferimento, la nostra Via Lattea è circa cinque volte più grande e 100 volte più massiccia di GN-108036, ma rende circa 30 volte in meno ogni anno.

title: DesignJet 450C colour cartridge alignment - DesignJet repairs
description:
How to run a colour cartridge alignment on a DesignJet 450C.
The cartridge alignment is run to resolve stepping or jagged lines produced by the cyan, magenta or yellow ink cartridges.
Sales, Support & Advice available at:
http://www.hpplotter.co.uk

This video shows the process used on the Designjet 400 series (including 430/450/455/488) to align any jagged lines being produced on some of the colours on the machine. An A4 sheet of paper is loaded into the printer and a Colour Cartridge Alignment sheet is produced. This shows how the colours are printing. Ignore any minor defects when you check the sheet for the best image, shade in the alterations sheet as shown on the video and reload the sheet face down with the arrow pointing into the printer. Select the setup button on the panel for the Designjet to look for the changes, it will then write them to the electronics module on the machine to resolve any stepped or jagged images you may have had.

title: Tutorial Photoshop Cs5 - Effetto infrarossi in B/N e a colori
description:
Nella fotografia tradizionale, tanto tempo fa, bisognava affidarsi esclusivamente ai filtri fotografici per realizzare determinati effetti che altrimenti non sarebbe stato possibile ottenere. La ripresa ad infrarosso permette di ottenere degli effetti molto suggestivi. Ad esempio, usando Filtri IR si accentuano dei particolari non visibili, la foschia si riduce sensibilmente, il verde delle foglie di un paesaggio si vede molto più chiaramente.

Questo genere di ripresa si effettua ponendo un filtro dedicato davanti all'obiettivo fotografico. L'infrarosso è una radiazione invisibile all'occhio umano.

title: 2012 Lexus LFA Nürburgring Package (2011 Geneva Auto Show)
description:
* 50 Units Available
* Nürburgring Race Car Influenced Styling and Performance
* 562 Horsepower and Quicker Gear Changes


TORRANCE, Calif. (May 10, 2010) -- Lexus announced today it will offer a limited edition Nürburgring Package to LFA customers.

"This Nürburgring Package builds on the track-ready Lexus supercar with styling cues from the 24 Hours of Nürburgring prototype LFA racecar," said Mark Templin, Lexus Division group vice president and general manager. "Driving enthusiasts will also appreciate the Nürburgring Package's performance enhancements that were proven on the legendary German track."

The 4.8L V10 engine for Nürburgring Package equipped LFA's will produce 562 horsepower, 10 more horsepower than the standard high-performance LFA. The gear-shift time has been reduced by 0.05 seconds to only 0.15 seconds for even faster gear changes.

The Nürburgring Package is limited to only 50 units out of the 500 LFA hand-assembled for global distribution. It will also have the following features:

# A sport-tuned suspension, exclusive black mesh-type wheels and dedicated high-grip tires for better handling;
# And a larger front spoiler and fixed rear wing for improved high speed down force.

This limited edition LFA will be available in four exterior colors -- whitest white, orange, black and matte black complemented by a choice of three interior colors -- black, red, and violet. All come with a carbon fiber center console and door trim. The Nürburgring Package will carry a Manufacturer's Suggested Retail Price (MSRP) of $70,000. Matte black will carry an additional cost of $20,000. The standard LFA carries a MSRP of $375,000.

In addition to the Nürburgring vehicle specifications, a package of special privileges is included in association with the Nürburgring course itself. The perks comprise, but are not limited to, private parking, co-pilot ride, one night at the Lindner Congress and Motorsport Hotel Nürburgring, private training with Nürburgring chief driving instructor, a Nürburgring branded jacket, as well as a one-year annual pass valid for driving on the Nordschleife and admission to ring°werk leisure park.

title: Красивый отдых - Египет. Подводный мир Шарм эль шейх
tags: ['красивый отдых', 'подводный мир', 'кораллы египет', 'шарм эль шейх', 'египет отпуск', 'море', 'пляжи египта', 'отпуск в египте', 'Sharm El-Sheikh (City/Town/Village)', 'Egypt (Country)']
description:
Мой заработок на отдыхе в Тайланде - http://myrezultat.ru
О подводном мире Красного моря ходят легенды. По красоте и разнообразию кораллов, морской флоры и фауны ему нет равных. Протянувшиеся вдоль всего египетского побережья коралловые рифы являются своеобразным жизненным центром, привлекающим множество рыб. Поражает разнообразие форм кораллов, которые могут быть круглыми, плоскими, разветвленными, а также иметь другие фантастические формы и цветовую гамму - от нежно-желтого и розового до коричневого и синего. Но цвет сохраняют только живые кораллы, после смерти они теряют мягкие покровные ткани и остается только белый кальциевый скелет. По египетским законам колонии кораллов разрушать нельзя.

Mingle Media TV and our Red Carpet Report host Jessie Pridemore were invited to cover the the 67th Emmy Awards Costume Design Nominee Reception hosted by Television Academy Peer Group Governors Sue Bub and Terry Ann Gordon and the FIDM Museum.

The event honored this year’s nominees with a certification and launched the FIDM Museum’s Ninth Annual Outstanding Art of Television Costume Design Exhibition. 

Save the Date: The 67th Primetime Emmy Awards, hosted by Andy Samberg, airs live Sunday, September 20 (8:00 PM ET / 5:00 PM PT) on FOX from the Nokia Theatre L.A. LIVE in Los Angeles. For more info, please visit http://www.emmys.com

About FIDM Museum’s Ninth Annual Outstanding Art of Television Costume Design Exhibition

title: ► Audi RS 7 Piloted Driving: AWESOME!!!
tags: ['youcar', 'review', 'test', 'drive', 'automobile', 'horsepower', 'spec', 'specifications', 'engine', 'performance', 'price', 'neue', 'Audi RS 7', 'Audi', 'Audi RS7', 'RS 7', 'automated driving', 'automated', 'piloted driving', 'piloted', 'autonomous', 'driving', 'demo', 'demonstration', 'Audi RS', 'Turbo', 'V8 engine', 'race track', 'Audi RS 6', 'Audi RS 5', 'Audi RS 4', 'Audi RS 8', 'Audi RS 3', '2015', 'Audi RS 1', 'Audi RS 2']
description:
The Audi RS 7 piloted driving concept car is a technology platform with which Audi is exploring the possibilities of piloted driving at its most dynamic. On Friday, October 17 and Sunday, October 19 – prior to the start of the last DTM race – the concept car will complete one lap on the Hockenheim ring without a driver. The large, five-door coupe is largely identical to the production model, but its electromechanical power steering, the brakes, the throttle valve and the eight-speed tiptronic that distributes the power to the mechanical quattro drive system are controlled automatically.
There are two primary technological considerations during piloted driving at the physical limit: the highly precise orientation of the vehicle on the road and absolute control of the vehicle at the handling limits.

The technology platform uses specially corrected GPS signals for orientation on the track. Accurate down to a centimeter, these differential GPS data are transmitted to the vehicle via WLAN according to the automotive standard and redundantly via high-frequency radio. Parallel to this, 3D camera images are compared in real time against graphical information stored on board. The system searches in each of the countless individual images for several hundred known features, such as building patterns behind the track, which it then uses as additional positioning information.
Control of the vehicle at the handling limits is another outstanding feature of the Audi RS 7 piloted driving concept car. Comprehensive on-board networking coupled with the highly precise control of all actors relevant to driving enable the technology platform to drive at the physical limits. The Audi engineers intensively investigated piloted driving at the handling limits, putting the technology platform through several thousand test kilometers on a variety of routes.

To demonstrate its capabilities, the Audi RS 7 piloted driving concept car will drive a clean racing line at the Hockenheimring – with full throttle on the straights, full braking before the corners, precise turn-in and perfectly metered acceleration when exiting the corners. Forces of over 1.3 g occur during braking, and lateral acceleration in the corners can reach 1.1 g. Tests on the track in Hockenheim suggested an expected top speed of 240 km/h (149.1 mph) and a lap time of 2 minutes and 10 seconds.

The race track is also the most demanding test bed for production when it comes to piloted driving. The future systems must also work extremely precisely and with zero errors in critical situations. They therefore must be capable of properly assessing the current situation even at the physical limit. This test bed provides the Audi engineers with a variety of insights for production development, such as for the development of automatic avoidance functions in critical driving situations.

description:

Thank you for using the AT&T Business YouTube channel. We hope that this has helped you resolve your issue, and we appreciate any feedback on the video's content or helpfulness. Please send us a direct message or leave a comment on the video.

This tutorial is for use with BlackBerry Handheld Software 7.0 devices.

If you have not been able to find the information you need through AT&T's online support sites please check the following BlackBerry™ online support sites:

BlackBerry™ Forums: http://go-att.us/YTBlackBerryForums 

BlackBerry™ Twitter: @BlackBerryHelp http://go-att.us/YTBlackBerryTwitter 

BlackBerry™ Answers: http://go-att.us/YTBlackBerryAnswers 

BlackBerry™ Facebook: http://go-att.us/YTBlackBerryFacebook 

BlackBerry™ YouTube: http://go-att.us/YTBlackBerryYouTube 
Video Script: 
Send, Receive, or Delete a Text Message (SMS) or Picture Message with the BlackBerry® Torch™ 9860. 

Welcome to AT&T How to videos.

Today we will show you how to Send, Receive, or Delete a Text Message (SMS) or Picture Message with the BlackBerry® Torch™ 9860.

First we will show you how to send a text or picture message
From the Home screen, open the All tray and select Text Messages
Now select Compose Text Message
Here enter the 10-digit mobile number of the recipient in the "To" field
Please Note: If sending a message to an international number enter "011" or enter a "+ sign" followed by the correct country code and number. (Example: "011441234567" or "+441234567". It is not possible to send a text message to an email address with a BlackBerry®
If sending a text message to a contact from the address book, type in the name and select the desired contact
Please Note: BES users can select Lookup to search the corporate global address list
If multiple numbers are associated with the contact, scroll to and select the desired number.
To add more recipients, enter the 10 digit mobile number or type the desired name to add a contact from the address book in the "To" field
You can now enter the desired text
 Please Note: To insert an attachment, select the paperclip icon
Now press the Send icon

Now we will show you how to receive and reply to a message
From the Home screen, open the All tray and select Text Messages
From the text message screen, highlight and select the desired message
You can now enter the desired reply
When completed, press the Send icon

Finally we will show you how to delete a message
From the text messages screen, scroll to and highlight the desired message
Now press the Menu key, and then select Delete
To confirm deletion, select Delete. The message will now be deleted.



If further assistance is needed feel free to contact our online Business Support Team at www.att.com/biz.  If accessing the site for the first time you will need to enter your device model and click "Go". 

Thank you for choosing AT&T.
